casebody.data:
Raul Vega v. Department of Liquor Control (13377)

Dupont, C. J., and Laveky and Hennessy, Js.

Argued April 19 decision released May 16, 1995 Brian Thomas Walsh, for the appellant (plaintiff). Sharon M. Hartley, assistant attorney general, with whom, on the brief, was Richard Blumenthal, attorney general, for the appellee (defendant). Per Curiam.

The judgment is affirmed.
